{"tid":1954452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府飛行服務隊直升機失事原來係沙士個年","createTime":"2020-04-01T23:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:56:50.000Z","uid":13745,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8742c1eef4fecb66fb36a0ab4691b70bd3f0d970","tid":1954452,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:13:20.000Z","msg":"B-HRX墜毀事故是香港政府飛行服務隊於1993年成立以來首宗墜機導致人員殉職的事故。事故發生於2003年8月26日晚上，一架政府飛行服務隊EC-155B1直昇機（登記編號B-HRX）在執行一個甲類疏散運送死傷者任務（Type A Casevac）時，於新界大嶼山伯公坳附近的山頭（位置為22&deg;14.9&prime;N 113&deg;56.5&prime;E）墜毀，兩名機員罹難。民航處的調查報告將事件列為「可控飛行撞地個案」<br />\n<br />\n今年新沙士就有解放軍直升機失事"},{"pid":"eda3c078541eb97f19c6058f38837b260f0a8ff4","tid":1954452,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140826/52826950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140826%2F52826950&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=62de0c20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140826%2F52826950&h=aadc6bf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140826/52826950</a>"},{"pid":"b9686d6675e1f5701c22644174c98b87e85789fa","tid":1954452,"uid":291338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"30號有霧有雨，根據目視飛行規則，能見度太低應該唔飛得，不過人哋軍隊係咪有另類做法就佢哋先至知"},{"pid":"cbd883fa6fcea3b7ca361e0cc53018af77f28524","tid":1954452,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9686d6675e1f5701c22644174c98b87e85789fa","tid":1954452,"uid":291338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"30號有霧有雨，根據目視飛行規則，能見度太低應該唔飛得，不過人哋軍隊係咪有另類做法就佢哋先至知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:57:46.000Z","msg":"唔信蛀港老解會跟足VFR同IFR呢啲規則飛 <br />\n果日嘅天氣跟VFR就唔會飛到去出事果一帶啦<br />\n而IFR緊嘅話 撞咗機CAD實會即時知出咗事唔駛等到隔咗成